&lt;/em&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;由于外国旅游业和抵制美国产品的回调，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;美国经济今年将&lt;/strong&gt;损失数十亿美元，这增加了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lw_qGzy3Z7f7qzVf6oDMdAUtT6AtECDKPSCiUJFcXA3ekBeumP0YhfiUtusC2cTYbTis8-14zap3-wsvTdPv3KaiQHDfqiBCDRQwKOXF_QNtCPDEUHn9-dMjH0Zstknp1o1y-xiCMqPYBKlC-2CfREtu4U3_59Avanq1YyPsdl4xF4VrNQ9Tze49TxD30lAQvMeEnI81fZrom6mplFJohu9-xsQu-srjuPHU1GyY_DuX0SObZQBal1MhzRRaJXhM2rm3q16jJ6r8J9dHA43_oeTa0g90IBIhQdhtdooJK4jppzwGrK5d8AJhExeI80sPhLkVFbeKOMpUWHBpU2j1i63fPlMG9nVSoqbqnfv4iB0WUV8RwsOp9UWPWYI/rjUAsX2AdWI6WMeiJrhsy7l-7-1rmGu4/8" target="_blank"&gt;越来越多的逆风&lt;/a&gt;将衰退风险提高。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;根据国际贸易管理局的数据，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;非公民乘飞机的到达&lt;/strong&gt;在三月份从一年前下降了近10％。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;高盛&lt;/strong&gt;估计，在最坏的情况下，今年的旅行减少和抵制量减少，今年的抵制可能占国内生产总值的0.3％，即近900亿美元。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;在重新思考他们的度假计划的人中&lt;/strong&gt;，加拿大人是在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对该国征收惩罚性关税之后，对南方的邻居保持警惕，并建议它&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ZRce4ORED22gX1pcdbJrJ_ZcoDnB3Z0Kx2JVJDlowqrz-IQ277D-5NdvZ7tytOc5syOrpwE3RUPFu4SCNbR4SEKBkLWxgYSSmxZckOQaRGAGPbWqMrgPOhhH6mXPXn8nG2xLl9y9rrNbuYz2fj--cWJ3bafzdvgPHoQj_EuxAYJLu-omrkO8QNjPyiXfM2gJeiTBPegivNRcHZYu_nohwuXX0qQCuuh-JqMn_Wh7BOSBgZMAoN6iwpNSLv0A8xW4G6S7BAn188-qcJEmPbK3h67XpMKptHMF8kw953oLzcA2wTNsJYmmo1W5mhKFOPln9_mJfri2RfhSw8_6yM1DCqow31cPhYGCXsr3eyDetvejy7bQK6XsknkTDoY/r6G9kgDhDRMZAlXui2XssGq1YEgk2TFR/8" target="_blank"&gt;应该成为美国第51个州&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;边境的敌对情绪&lt;/strong&gt;增加了对美国旅行的压力，报道了对外国国民的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/k2zGGamOBiSGdiWGvXaA3q1DAxtiZLEPG1qLllVHB26z_bC_VULqWL3Y3qEBGxJ__YV6uS7dJNN1jaCbQmr8VSoFYYaE1ds8MGACDFU4SIm6aGTS_M3sYS8iNuHMexJ3rKZkq_7IPqIHw6BXw6w4O6awvx0caiPiuMl6cc2pUTDJ05f1424luwk1REci88Hh8fCqeyISDGQxfO0GGgts4U44BBbkzRGyqm0mArBZgnKcI2_yld5XXIKLSYLZjX2R9Ch2cpl6qBAlmufwKJCKBCOr3zTuFNA2WDk51Vr-2P9D4iqxwgwRUAEwTDlLQERAs32h-kVhO0BOMw_z5pbrgwdwdVQqdO0RgxFaFqCUEpoSBfBrik5ks5qHRWE/eEB-x-CTArQuXwWYiDeATRCMQoeJgJrc/8" target="_blank"&gt;苛刻和长期拘留&lt;/a&gt;的报道。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;另一个令人震惊的来源：&lt;/strong&gt;一些加拿大高管正在建议员工不要前往美国旅行，并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/bCBq0qvSk1vSKAfe4woHKHH180GNRHTgAQ5AlWOW1J--ynJLWYn5NPOHfJ_dS3gOOltO1ZRLYsm7m9AHdGnrdX13pdRu4-D1TWg2PgORsNJc-n9wfNEFYDXwd9vUhvivzUSJOQ3Jw-vRFQy2ly96SUNd791Fo8YVhDHgAJlCIAj7wHv_N0Ns9L0Wkz4gg9ZHX3ER2MCMt8Kior-LmAtlTFM7Y_lBP822bgZY3RZTD-d7HKimKGKYUhvENKuOBCxpdq-2KbTPM3nuz7ToSASEyl9iPSL8MGMZMAFhm3SpYofYlzbrxIuEMvqkYYwx8V9XRV2q_0M8rr3Xkq0UVtTSb4YyE9-ssJT__tjiJL2PZkTD5TkhEZXu3bwexdA/toixPJsWAmPLeSat7HEWnumxVjxCuaCO/8" target="_blank"&gt;拿起燃烧器的电话&lt;/a&gt;- 如果他们决定去，那几乎没有一个没有个人数据的设备。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/OEYvDHCSYINXj8CLHqcmSA_fVnqV_mYKe-mQZItDrVuDCU-sxafQ9SrAD6ITRIpObfHa_xk8zbvSfscaTuQl-0AS6qVI_4zdqY4KJQ7KZQqH46updSTJcOsSYmeuFIDOl1lywH9quSFJ83isnKTmXF3DHA00BkGMOdtkJR7x_bRPK3qUUUmPodjFkCTr2L7GPS_QJvsk7w8BQOBx57rgvFodxDpIuc7LulUvYlTFVpSjYEcEf536u4eit2vyozPGU8arxfopVqX-pC02C-8CEdaueLm41QS6VkKyLt2s77w_LWnufWvx1lXKYTd6bC81QAFlBSLu9eXuS5rdENeqW_5ca3c6CujoPV4RX0wDPMFdYjc8nPsGLvwKNUg/FKf5f5Ptv6G4NijuvjqNN2NePeqPQKd_/8" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i7cAIHylrnzw/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWi