aWNDJK3Va8XQ_vDhyxFZG1SJQh2mh8073qTGVn2awqKV5JPVyePCAV2eEsl95HoIOAeqpIbatVqrJtPPX_OSQklwr6fSnMhlu0B0G23UKT--pGfpGGvXhFaC4AMtw9NY7YHRvKJ5aMoASxTQVCFDU2P9MtZfnc_UkjbhrOjoQpFANwYUpmH6q0wIG6tzUChDLwKSK1uoxva8w3u-5JU4s5o-8OfO4NKcasQeCzXbmUgH6mWVDW2lYVH7vPyGBNCL7uuGpAhxf0OIWejEG_xf9N5ge3jCL_K6Pi9fP6ELTxAA/mZ-FWowhWCCTsZviGdlZ2lDoARBD194I/8" title="启动贸易调查"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;由商务部领导的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/TMkJS6u6XHeBMb2-3XkZGG5NFSXhleuZMpgfXQ1-OYiLCmOe1vzcsMzOl5_047QhCa_WVmiQPzIxpn6aWNDJK3Va8XQ_vDhyxFZG1SJQh2mh8073qTGVn2awqKV5JPVyePCAV2eEsl95HoIOAeqpIbatVqrJtPPX_OSQklwr6fSnMhlu0B0G23UKT--pGfpGGvXhFaC4AMtw9NY7YHRvKJ5aMoASxTQVCFDU2P9MtZfnc_UkjbhrOjoQpFANwYUpmH6q0wIG6tzUChDLwKSK1uoxva8w3u-5JU4s5o-8OfO4NKcasQeCzXbmUgH6mWVDW2lYVH7vPyGBNCL7uuGpAhxf0OIWejEG_xf9N5ge3jCL_K6Pi9fP6ELTxAA/mZ-FWowhWCCTsZviGdlZ2lDoARBD194I/8" title="启动贸易调查"&gt;探测器&lt;/a&gt;。同时，总统说，他正在探索&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/JavuNsAfwFKtM6QftrDioH3q9ZjF8WNl87AVlj1zMiHXwyWbQ9whhhBSYXqnjLeE94ds06GKNWu2YSbBSuy-ifHrd5zTqC5TK0EjNKB1CEnkEBN9k68dFg8XUty3Yjyx7FdoT3OSnOC5cWS_Ifp4ivQj8VrvSINe7SChAt_EAcUGzuuaG5wpGUizC0-Q4qfu0AHUWRbIyyg7tt4yOHmQLIACiylPR-9X3Oh28H7EjnZ8MyoH2FHwXlkLnQ_AzwNybXR53jAPoobKx8uDJbmBuUNBummFt4sa4pwuCHHwykMewJViDxronb7mvjeyFEucDc45o0obTzFiQzCBGWwAYXbLU1tiZ6AJtzOndqxTW8BS_0TWZosBD-sIoS0/NHz4bwZO6jiy1lDXDsatTOQsdWMmphcs/8" title="可能的临时豁免"&gt;可能暂时豁免&lt;/a&gt;进口车辆和汽车零件，以使公司有更多时间建立美国制造设施。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在今年的&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;第一次海外旅行中&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;，中国总统习近平呼吁越南共同反对“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/oJNtB5aknbnA9Z6uvERvi5mfOXU81ssLwvX9t9YrjVodcGbMXy8MBLtEA5LvRg5Sjbzp0WHC-mwlvdeckNPhrxQ6odfr9WbZJEkPQxzYHj3tpsZcWaCRZpfVBF2LX3vRHf0RPGUNI6-FTf_OeXRTQbBaehMR69chm-LapT2trlEyY4AjDqgoekR-rjrroJkGdzsFepg9xjxRxWevihuvwbeniW2Hg2ISmUbebJxCHsEwOcuroFqBQRoOGznzuI3dZUfdA38PZiARQVvr7yhrRBysWS-XXtTtFNvzKcFdh0zTuL_eJIbrKJfHYd8FvswNb5IpZ0nRSn1VEHbVZgbEIQKAPedBA4Qf9b_JbAdGItdrVlD84Crs_c7bTHk/HhVYLvmpZXoTn-CeazPhlVyBmyjMSrQe/8"&gt;单方面欺凌&lt;/a&gt;”，以维持全球自由贸易和供应链的稳定性。同时，北京关于香港事务的高级官员&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/HDRybL-NbTd41uxfPRiOCsSGikHA-zd6Rf2ISsOWZ6UK-6ft6fX7X0cZK27tqXgkEkX-MoX5xs9BvwiKE62Ww2p0cNrpRtbVmfNrBo_teUz-QeesnDqmP6C4qhUwSvnYNwn7JKnBUFp7Y_BQbLT5dBENM9u1VQGvv1kaRRi_DRV0Q0wJ7A3tK2JggsqUzYhUxgAtZ_ixKcYH8-Y78NFUeQGDurJhrH5J16k3jgdnXfVRb0J96Udt2jh_CuHau5_5_ca8GMazv4TmIiwBMTO6URlYhesyqCkG-JZ4w2am62weoD4eeXRZ_lzksVDp8dFx7w5aUcVVecem-v1Ac6LbfBGuPg0moBwQHt5U9lCXD1GBJGYpXG90MOqg0xY/HnxUr44kVKcsz602tbU2I1Kh4rKSYwzR/8"&gt;对特朗普大肆抨击&lt;/a&gt;，称他的关税战争是攻击中国人民的福祉。有影响力的人&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/hSP8IcyNNqTNqpd9-itxcnaIBbPCoNIkpc7t4KU5yKFaitrX7wWHrDw_iSswGknvcklbishuTXVOak6J6GaWiSYXVlOq7KFNctb_pOkI3YIQsopd-WrwPNJCjYE_Y9DNPzTBHaqrVQ6s6kPnF1DgB0n-Wdi5AZweNsjwgwSg0Ssh1pEMZ5l7QeN8DP7F3kGvXFFI9mWxiwTJ9ELH1V-cIKtDqcysWgbtqk99Jw6wcZ5qsS6qEAcpYV6KXBozvIbkEAHdQdaiH9Ws27U1ZS4NTatTEaoODtrDey3NnS96W-AI5-Ys6ivaFVWSdJNxC--zq7s_s7ZyQhpgTEC1jJ8x6vdQFP7pLDORgJz_As4GhlvnVsU54eHg0mept2M/oDyc0Zxh9MJm3rzFv9l4uSca8pyizzDz/8"&gt;嘲笑了蒂克托克（Tiktok）的税款&lt;/a&gt;，消息人士称，中国已&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Q59UnxyJ31PvXCFKI6it6JDzs3BtCQ5gDYv--zojJYH4NHjJS9hnwTvl1JUYbqkbbMSB2ySiwgIXqJjKU7YDLJjt8eE6bvKGq2fGEfOambzOdq4ZfxoZa0AGZ1OhW6ZUGoMeln4ePFH7byYzx8M9DEmN9d4FFf-_F768OqQKQNTAkur4KELMdWV1zaHawHK2043vx96x_S9yo2ONefvrkeeQ3s1J-SZ-P2G04ICnsXwUjZXyHfQ6scql0tyUWvb-6aeZ1sGK-qJpN_4Ht31wNh6fylFeHtJO7esWfONTQAp_xZN_Qe2dB7gXKiDH3cEJWg6Cc6Gq6i_MXd4tKk4KRWSnENMnkQnSPt0wNwRkH7owVy8Dp3lp4o6jD7E/LEONuZfsH6Uw6Y8VJPg1W-rGmvR3mSjk/8" target="_blank"&gt;下令其航空公司&lt;/a&gt;不采取任何交付波音飞机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）推出了&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;最近在债券市场上的抛售， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/VTuOqozx8yz9lh4eLL3VonNo9Yw17bBwkrC7kYOf-PiUFX4SxlurZizhyg3yhRytUnSw_NdxbG7RkspUq0o0l1PGdUGUOjfN77fUvRo0caJfIS_OIaqTRqJ35yQscbG6sFibx-8gzxPcMA6ndXfGY6qId4QUlBmknNSU2Y7Ss5liCR0-qMpW7aPRHWKsgW7X6W2TOI6v9QRfcQHn8uRrasMKKxwr6BdZOZBZGoF7wBgY6pPHAmZQSo3TZPY4HDmF5Ia5wRExh1vDKmEXx3xsPwgiQGK1n00_I7vEojwWXJ2htsNRaBNrn3Ua6kORsIweDRH7oyOX_nlzW5cUHxEeI7IPJpWnMcagAPmZrFNR1im55mxzjz8hvt68VrA/UO77SVVj9ArmrxxfPPVurWvDUGTg5X0d/8" title="拒绝投机"&gt;拒绝猜测&lt;/a&gt;外国国家正在抛弃其对美国国债的持股，同时宣布他的部门有工具可以在需要时解决位置。持有10年国库券的风险溢价已&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/oWHu0qJbg7ZHC6TyenPAdNDNlIJHLKZY8EKik-31xvR-k36Bt12pMTzsjahbmV8vfFOc1uo_b0BpOj5LcYaP9FL6PkwomuXXq__ARGeygvfY0v_4Yg9QMAWHxyZ1Wg7JcIbr4mN3uoqb2iODFHO7pkGRbKYYryUdacKfSQeI4NJyuicAfQ4YPb4ilpYL47hTEgwv98rQ-hacW0WUXRtDNT5lJsuc7NAXjs_-_FireoHdf3JtMKmsORqwOtlNa4duC0-4Besv6Wim9ZmlgxVlP40DOvfxBjd4voIzQqckNhfU6TTogUVTCewrwxDmw2PgQCig18kN6DHQLs8ovpWhs0rHgQIn_Qj2nN5MTRfgD4D_AEk85T0n50Pqqo0/SC0e-Oi_ZsjtH6vZZ_mVcvNRB9HnxKwH/8" title="十年来最高"&gt;在十年来上升到最高&lt;/a&gt;，因为美国关税政策将使投资者对该国的政府债券有信心。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWy4v.nPQhGI/v0/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWy4v.nPQhGI/v0/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;观看：Bessent专门与布宜诺斯艾利斯的彭博社的Annmarie Hordern交谈。&lt;i&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16p