adding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;高盛股票交易员&lt;/strong&gt;在记录中发布了其季度收入最高的收入， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/o--zi2SmhTOlBfGM47wGWOKcWccAS0EbcnNXRLGLQXAqOWBLDaH9egUvZEtJ0PjQFJb8R6GenMINmCAPzEDFhxOFAXgiGmpkqX1R855PkHCAJu8LBOvmu18FKBhoQqYrcuP2NQAoj3-akl_IiUkJV1T02foKc-TEcb_yMHq6vI-cm7Aup651UG6UsiJPOFKU0EZZYwkUh-Of-k1uZTLeAgws4Vnq970drFNamfrVdm3TGc1DG1IxVn-BgdvxcyM1Qz3jNWIwqtjsN2ksqZeHpGJAh1CThZKY2Vdj_qQFW26XD-h5Wz0rI7Z5MqVaH5cCpcz30euam5-soipqAjKT-KwA-dPxeyUhF3I3QFGPpfklNq-wcNPhezdkclY/Gpk1oIzyK4qlwflAyJgLkXa8zLLe490l/8" target="_blank"&gt;这是全球贸易战引起的一波波动&lt;/a&gt;。一年前的前三个月，股票交易的收入从去年同期增长了27％，至41.9亿美元。从上周开始，结果是基于该行业的势头，当时高盛（Goldman）的同龄人在包括摩根大通（JPMorgan）和摩根士丹利（Morgan Stanley）在此期间还赢得了创纪录的股票交易拖运。他们在2024年为高盛（Goldman）创下了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/jHqZhHV2K3Lo0HLH0YAe8Nm3GCNhOOXoau__KjBTGax-wBhYfGh5tE15AHEpgmrZQeI-ePdNHBDW7j6NdUjt31b17fBJC4DKcg_o908d5GvVePFecQgxsC5xR5fZhQruoAob4a7PA8P0mtRqnh04ffqqtsILiB3UjCW8NIF06Mm2RaVQWjzGCWgwUl5OD5E0n_pK7tMkBhuAippDi9XuePlfgc25xcE8LLUZT_Lpe2RKfxlD-i8DB0W4CpA_OFuazHHWvddchVRKdkugnhFmuYVX3dFf-sZWVQ4mndD21wLRsbDttopoQYYhA1VcoCJpcPTzHVlNBCXUgj3Z5RxVWDKiLpTv-h5mTOOowLT6cQwR7K60kh2jAFdTrG8/cQACYmIa4enpsi4jxtUVer7YM35CEH-A/8" target="_blank"&gt;创纪录的一年&lt;/a&gt;，当时总部位于纽约的银行将其在该部门的收入提高了近50％。首席执行官戴维·所罗门（David Solomon）说：“尽管我们进入第二季度的操作环境与今年早些时候明显不同，但我们仍然对继续支持客户的能力充满信心。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/-nPMTsezPUZ-u8P1XsxXGyhlcqukXtz4DQFxyXsBoonlLgWmNw74Bao3mFtYKgMyNDV6r2vlYAMVCkATWSOrFEM4D1sUT7eKCjmyuqhpiaqmRM41JdbbWtHO7Cg3QiY5jecrYZfwxiyiq1Rr8Y_T8ItF9d4BUKgOXp00vshUAHg0OL3LxJyQ38LVz8-vYNDB9VfkNm7RmzW887H8j4lpsrUGlB2WwRBs0CN4_ddC4Vm1EPjeYKCvwa3ew49W3Wg--jH87weDu8Ta6ioHZ_FEHNaK1sY_YMXvJ-8w-6F7pvH0csHhB71tYn9VyGH846hBcLikmWWjRQcSGnuqBu6JYAFebHl8w5PUIBIO__G2Rm3fk3N-vxTt6Hm9V4k/TSeletzhFV8YvZmf6vZUOi63sQTmIJ_B/8" t